## Tool Integration Workflow

- [ ] 1. Audit the current tool ecosystem — what tools are in use and how they're connected
- [ ] 2. Identify gaps, redundancies, and manual workflows that could be automated
- [ ] 3. Define integration requirements — what data must flow between which tools
- [ ] 4. Research integration options — native integrations, middleware, APIs, automation platforms
- [ ] 5. Design the integrated workflow — how data moves, who owns each step
- [ ] 6. Implement the integration with testing and validation
- [ ] 7. Document the workflow and train the team

## Key Inputs
- Tools involved: {{tools}}
- Current workflow (problematic): {{current_workflow}}
- Integration goal: {{goal}}
- Budget/constraints: {{constraints}}
